{"title":"西方“自由”活现形","authors":["袁水拍"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西方“自由”活现形"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一个“新闻自由”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一个“人身自由”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大英帝国一向夸口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今在香港展览个够。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把新闻记者摔出大门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把教师学生赶出校舍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸黑偷袭中华中学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还施展出“特别训练过的拳头”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把照相机狠狠地踩烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕它使你们出乖露丑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连闪光灯也成了大敌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起被勇士们打在里头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"害怕得很啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胆怯而又下流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很不自由啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还吹什么牛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香港！香港！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸦片、特务、刽子手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大好山河被罪恶的殖民者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搅得又脏又臭！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}